OL,3,CResidents react to 'long overdue'
OL,4,Cairport runway upgrade
OL,6,FAlderney residents say they are widely
OL,7,Fhappy with the island's planned runway
OL,8,Fresurfacing, despite the site having
OL,9,Fto shut for up to five months during
OL,10,Fnext year's peak visitor season.
OL,12,FLast week, Guernsey States backed a
OL,13,F#24 million proposal for substantial
OL,14,Fupgrades to Alderney Airport, after
OL,15,Fyears of short-term mends to keep the
OL,16,Fasphalt runway operational.
OL,18,FOn-site construction is expected to
OL,19,Frun from April to September 2027, with
OL,20,Fthe airport being closed throughout
OL,21,Fthis period.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/6
