OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1772701496
OL,3,CResidents react to 'long overdue'
OL,4,Cairport runway upgrade
OL,6,FMany islanders are delighted with the
OL,7,Fplans, with one describing them as
OL,8,F"excellent news and a long time
OL,9,Fcoming".
OL,11,FOne resident says: "It's fantastic.
OL,12,FAlderney has been desperate for really
OL,13,Fgood connectivity, and it's just going
OL,14,Fto make life easier for islanders and
OL,15,Fvisitors alike."
OL,17,FAnother adds: "It's good that Guernsey
OL,18,Fis now paying for the maintenance it
OL,19,Fshould've done over the years."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
