OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1772701496
OL,3,CResidents react to 'long overdue'
OL,4,Cairport runway upgrade
OL,6,FIslanders have been assured that while
OL,7,Fthe airport is closed, medical
OL,8,Fevacuation flights will still be
OL,9,Fpossible by helicopter.
OL,11,FOtherwise, the majority of travel to
OL,12,Fand from the island is expected to
OL,13,Fhappen by sea while the airport is
OL,14,Fclosed.
OL,16,FAlderney Airport welcomes around
OL,17,F50,000 passengers each year.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
