PN,38404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1772701496
OL,3,CResidents react to 'long overdue'
OL,4,Cairport runway upgrade
OL,6,FThe majority of these visitors come
OL,7,Fduring the summer months, particularly
OL,8,Ffor events such as Alderney Week in
OL,9,FAugust and the island's literary
OL,10,Ffestival, which was cancelled in
OL,11,FFebruary, in part due to "travel
OL,12,Funcertainty".
OL,14,FAndrew Eggleston, President of
OL,15,FAlderney's Chamber of Commerce,
OL,16,Fexplains: "Obviously, there's going to
OL,17,Fbe frustration from businesses,
OL,18,Fespecially amongst the hospitality
OL,19,Fsector.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
