PN,38405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1772701496
OL,3,CResidents react to 'long overdue'
OL,4,Cairport runway upgrade
OL,6,F"But this will be a temporary blip ...
OL,7,FWe're future proofing the island for
OL,8,Fthe next 10, 20, 30 years."
OL,10,FAs well as resurfacing the runway, it
OL,11,Fwill also be widened from 18 to 23
OL,12,Fmetres, and its lighting and drainage
OL,13,Ffacilities will be improved.
OL,15,FIn 2024, Guernsey's previous Policy
OL,16,Fand Resources Committee scrapped plans
OL,17,Fto develop Alderney's Airport, after
OL,18,Fprojected costs spiralled to #37
OL,19,Fmillion.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/6
