OL,3,CResidents react to 'long overdue'
OL,4,Cairport runway upgrade
OL,6,FThis time around, politicians hope to
OL,7,Fkeep the project within budget by
OL,8,Flimiting its scope - including ruling
OL,9,Fout a runway extension and a new
OL,10,Fterminal.
OL,12,FAlderney Airport timeline:
